snippet.title: Can Androids Survive - LAUNCH TRAILER
snippet.description:
In 2143, a rogue AI commandeers the defense satellites surrounding a dead Earth, and blows up the Moon. This is how you do it.

Can Androids Survive is a new shortform sandbox mech FPS from the writer of Can Androids Pray.

BUY: https://xalaviermakeswords.itch.io/can-androids-survive
